title: Off the Hook Sushi
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese restaurant where staff will accommodate request for no egg, no fish sauce, etc. Offers a tofu tempura with ginger sauce as well veggie tempura, and sushi rolls that include tempura veggies as well as the normal assortment of raw veggies (avocado, asparagus, cucumber, pickled radish). The tempura batter is vegan though the fryer is shared with meatstuff. Could get a tofu saute with brown rice and small dishes of wakame, edamame, vegetable gyoza.
